{"tid":130652,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【差佬晒馬】前線警台上高喊：X你老母 台下歡呼叫好","createTime":"2017-02-22T14:05:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-22T17:31:17.000Z","uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1923eef95392788ab55f24041d7720ab647ca76c","tid":130652,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T14:05:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170222/large/1487770783_312d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170222%2Flarge%2F1487770783_312d.jpg&h=1ccdcd12&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n4個警察協會今晚聯合舉行的特別代表大會，除了獲建制陣營多名鷹派人物上台撐場，亦邀請不少前線警員上台分享，其中一名上台分享的前線警員大吐苦水，指執勤時經常被人侮辱，要「帶埋阿爸阿媽返工」，並即場示範平日辱警的情況，在台上爆Seed高喊「X你老母」，結果獲台下的伙計大聲歡呼叫好，網上媒體《立場新聞》所拍得的片段更顯示，台下隱約聽到有不少人跟着呼應「X你老母」。"},{"pid":"9c2a6ebdbf5167715b6387dc1de2fb117c7b7be2","tid":130652,"uid":85498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T14:06:12.000Z","msg":"慈母：歡迎屌我老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db415edca7813599907d449432396aba85b8b2b9","tid":130652,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T14:07:51.000Z","msg":"好叻咩，香港有邊個對客唔洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2df90781c8d0fde6fdaabcd7144f55be2627d91b","tid":130652,"uid":54576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T14:08:08.000Z","msg":"香港地大把人返工都係要帶老豆老母㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講到剩係得你哋班警察先係<br />\n好撚慘呀可？<br />\n咪撚搏同情啦屌！<br />\n成班喺度打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"321dfaee3e7876996dfcae7213f6f59e360a65c6","tid":130652,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T14:08:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.soomal.com/images/doc/20130930/00036000.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww